
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
Wa wa way, wa way<br />
Wa wa way, wa way</p>
<p>On my wings I want to take you to the sky<br />
And in my nakedness to kiss all that is mine<br />
I want to be your cupid of passion<br />
I want to be the mistress of your heart</p>
<p>I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours like the sun belongs to its shine<br />
I want to be yours like the river belongs to the sea</p>
<p>I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours like the honey of your kiss<br />
I want to be yours, I was born to love you</p>
<p>Wa wa way, wa way<br />
Wa wa way, wa way</p>
<p>I want to be the light that guides your way<br />
I want to take you to the sweet world of affection<br />
I want to bathe myself in your body of pleasure<br />
And the quench my thirst to have you</p>
<p>I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours like the sun belongs to its shine<br />
I want to be yours like the river belongs to the sea</p>
<p>I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours, oh&#8230;<br />
I want to be yours like the honey of your kiss<br />
I want to be yours, I was born to love you</p>
<p>Wa wa way, wa way<br />
Wa wa way, wa way<br />
Eu quero ser tua, oh, tua&#8230;</p>
